00:12:27.260 --> 00:12:28.110
Vila Wucheng?

00:12:37.110 --> 00:12:38.360
Finalmente, estão todos aqui.

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:40.560
Zhang Sheng.

00:12:40.570 --> 00:12:41.420
Wang Heng.

00:12:41.420 --> 00:12:42.930
Conspirou com os heróis errantes

00:12:42.930 --> 00:12:43.850
para derrubar o Tribunal.

00:12:43.940 --> 00:12:46.970
